node.text: The New Kentucky Fried Chicken Sandwich is HUGE, DELICIOUS, CRISPY, and only $3.99. See for yourself when you order on the KFC App!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kentucky Fried Chicken on June 22, 2021. May be an image of 6 people, french fries and indoor.

node.text: We are proud to announce that we are donating $275,000 to @bbbsamerica! KFC’s donation to BBBSA will provide meals to 5,000 newly matched Bigs and Littles this summer and support the organization’s workforce mentoring programs.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kentucky Fried Chicken on June 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Did you celebrate the summer solstice with dance and lute yesterday? If you didn’t, quickly repent by leaving a fried chicken offering to the sun or it will go away for an entire chicken harvest!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kentucky Fried Chicken on June 20, 2021. May be an image of food and text that says 'HAPPY FRIED FATHER'S DAY COLONEL SANDERS' ORIGINAL RECIPE Kentucky Fried Chicken'.

node.text: We tried to build a bird feeder, but, wooden you know it, it came out as a dad feeder. Happy Father’s Day!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kentucky Fried Chicken on May 28, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: I sure hope you folks enjoy your extra-long but not too long weekend with extra short, but not too short shorts.
